==English==
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[fearn]]''
===Noun===
'''fern'''

# Any of a group of some twenty thousand [[species]] of [[vascular]] [[plant]]s classified in the Division ''[[Pteridophyta]]'' (formerly known by some as ''[[Filicophyta]]'') that lacks [[seed]]s and [[reproduce]]s by [[shed]]ding [[spores]] to [[initiate]] an [[alternation]] of [[generation]]s.

